description:
After giving our last episode some well-deserved breathing room since becoming the most successful installment in the series yet, we are back with a brand new episode courtesy of DEBBIE, one of the resident DJs and main-men behind the Chicago-based collective, <a href="http://donttrusthumans.wordpress.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Don’t Trust Humans</a>. The next hour is the live recording of his set when we hosted him (alongside Qbot) at our last event a few weeks ago, <a href="http://www.residentadvisor.net/event.aspx?541563" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Erratic VS Don’t Trust Humans</a>. We are very happy to feature this mix as it is deep and excellent; and full with exquisite, shrewd material intended for “just brains.” This is Debbie Live, ENJOY!&#13;
