Changing gears from our last episode, we now go on a deep, shrewd, and ethereal journey provided by none other than <a href="http://www.prologuemusic.blogspot.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Prologue's</a> label boss, TOM BONATY. We are very proud and excited to have him be the starring guest in Podcast Episode #80 as mixes from this man come few and apart, and they are always unique and very special. In true fashion, evoking the label's motto, the next hour is an introspective exploration through the mind, sound, and space - taking you 10,000 leagues far beyond imagined. There is no tracklist, so just make sure to absorb it as it was intended to - sonically, whole, without preconceptions. Now sit back, relax, and enjoy!&#13;
