Hailing from Rotterdam, our next guest is a superb DJ who has been playing since his teens during the 90s, and producing his energetic and characteristic sound for more than a decade, <a href="https://www.facebook.com/destroyaliens" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">CHARLTON</a>. He has an eclectic and versatile mixing style, and on his latest studio mix for us he delivered an amazing 1-hour mix (showcasing some of his recent material on <a href="https://www.facebook.com/MindTripRec" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">MindTrip</a> and <a href="https://www.facebook.com/mordrecords" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Mord</a>), spanning 30 tracks of unique, classic techno. There's not much else to say than to let the music speak for itselt. This one is a doozy, folks. Enjoy!&#13;
