There is really not much to say about our next guest that hasn't been said before - born and bred in LA, started DJing in his teens, part of the long-standing Droid family, techno prodigy and current forerunner in the genre, alter ego extraordinaire.... we are talking about TRUNCATE.&#13;
&#13;
Most commonly know as Audio Injection, as well as for his pivotal affiliation across Droid and CLR over the last 5+ years, he came up with the Truncate alias and project 2 years ago. This was intended to be more of a personal outlet for him to release a deeper, funkier, Detroit-influenced, and stripped-down version of techno, but it has taken the techno community by storm since. From releases to remixes, gigs to podcasts, shirts to stickers, his alter ego is currently at an all-time high, and we are delighted David took time from his busy schedule to put together this exclusive studio mix for us.&#13;
&#13;
As you are about to listen, the next hour is the epitome of what his project is all about - deep, jackin', rhythmic techno - that grabs you by the core and it is as much of a body workout as it is the minds. Without further adieu, ladies and gentlemen, this is Truncate. &#13;
