We have quite a treat for you for our 55th episode - Coming straight from Berlin, founder of the acclaimed Vault Series and very talented producer, we are happy to present SUBJECTED. He is one of the new-generation techno producers and has been leaving his mark now for the past several years. &#13;
&#13;
He established the label in 2010 as a home for his productions for him as well as for his counterparts, Moerbeck and Sawlin (whom Subjected usually plays live with). His debut album, <a href="http://www.residentadvisor.net/review-view.aspx?id=12923" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Zero</a>, was released earlier this year on <a href="http://www.beatport.com/label/vault-series/15527/tracks?perPage=150" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Vault Series</a> and is truly a masterpiece – deep, raw, gritty, driving techno. &#13;
&#13;
In the next 2 hours, you will be able to get a taste of his style and more; this is part of a live recording when he played at Groningen, Netherlands, earlier this month. In the words of the man himself, this is <i>“music from under the surface, designed in the shadows, to be consumed in the darkness."</i> Enjoy!&#13;
