For our 11th episode we are honored to present Forward Strategy Group (composed by Al Matthews and Patrick Walker). This comes as a special 2-hour recording extracted from their live US debut in New York City a couple weeks back, where they took the privileged crowd on a 5-hour journey.&#13;
